程序包 zx.soft.utils.expiringmap

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    EntryLoader<K,V>
    Loads entries on demand.
    ExpirationListener<K,V>
    A listener for expired object events.
    ExpiringEntryLoader<K,V>
    Loads entries on demand, with control over each value's expiry duration (i.e. variable expiration).
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Assert  
    ExpiringMap<K,V>
    A thread-safe map that expires entries.
    ExpiringMap.Builder<K,V>
    Builds ExpiringMap instances.
    ExpiringMap.ExpirationListenerConfig<K,V>
    Provides an expiration listener configuration.
    ExpiringMap.ExpiringEntry<K,V>
    Expiring map entry implementation.
    ExpiringValue<V>
    A value which should be stored in an ExpiringMap with optional control over its expiration.
    NamedThreadFactory
    Named thread factory.
  • 枚举概要
